framebuffer system monitor with truetype font handling, 32bit colors and
histograms.

depends: freetype2, libseccomp (currently only with musl, check the makefile to enable it)

run it like:
./mon sda eth1:

no configuration, stuff gets compiled, check monky.c.

screenshot can be seen here: https://www.ctrlc.hu/~stef/monky.png
